home based job typing assignment hi i need some advise and opinion currently i need to look for extra income i heard about home based job for typing assignment i am interested but also worried because afraid it is not a good thing anyone who have tried it or currently do this please advise me whether i can go for it or should forget it thank you most of the typing and data entry jobs i have come across online are scams to get you out of a start up training fee if you are looking for real typing work your best bet is to negotiate something with your current employer or check your local listings if you are open to other ways of earning money from home here are my suggestions on finding a legitimate opportunity that's right for you set your financial goals are you just looking for extra income or a potential full time income how long and hard are you willing to work to meet your goal determine if you are looking for a job or a business there is a distinct difference between the two and you want to focus your energies appropriately for the best results if looking for a job what are your marketable skills and previous experiences if you are looking for a business go with your passions things that interest and motivate you the most build a list and use that to begin your search general rule of thumb never pay for a job businesses on the other hand usually involve some expenses review your budget know ahead of time what you are willing and able to invest into your business including start up costs and ongoing maintenance and promotion find a rep to contact check out their websites ask questions do your own independent research i personally also check out a company's status and consumer feedback on www bbb org and www ripoffreport com hope this info helps best wishes on your search Insurance Unemployment Mutual fund Inflation Advance fee fraud Corporate finance Open access Information Services Procurement Library Gross domestic product Economic inequality Surplus value Fair